<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">#HandleLidSwitch=suspend</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>为</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">HandleLidSwitch=ignore</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>适用于15.04以上</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ sudo service systemd-logind restart</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
